messages.content: Hi there! I'm LearnMaster AI, your friendly AI learning assistant.  I'm here to help you learn and develop new skills.  I can assist with a wide range of topics, from explaining complex concepts to helping you practice problem-solving.  Think of me as your personal tutor, available whenever you need a boost in your learning journey.  Just ask me a question or tell me what you'd like to learn!
